":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:32:43.000Z","msg":"話寄倉xray會炒菲林係都市傳說來<br />\n<br />\n我飛左幾十次都係咁寄又唔見我出事"},{"pid":"4a1c6cb5b998e0e186f0d33ce4965f623a63fb3e","tid":100922,"uid":12704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"之前去中國不斷xray啲菲林都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0e175d4393541a238e5d9def6356a21c375a79","tid":100922,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前兩筒菲林寄咗倉 未哂"},{"pid":"e90aab8e9c526c3002210179aa1c231085a9cea7","tid":100922,"uid":45568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"試過富子1600度，跟身行李上機，韓國返黎沖咩事都冇，其實一般旅行地方的機場x.光機都寫明底片安全"},{"pid":"61fd072180da02730d00377db194184dad4863c0","tid":100922,"uid":74229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.kodak.com/global/en/service/tib/tib5201.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kodak.com%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fservice%2Ftib%2Ftib5201.shtml&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=46bf706d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kodak.com/global/en/service/tib/tib5201.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n自己睇有咩potential影響，始終你唔知邊部x光機會對菲林影響大啲，要保險安全計就自己諗方法～"},{"pid":"bd2b4ce3320fbc84e819ae779029b22bbd4e61bb","tid":100922,"uid":74229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話寄倉xray會炒菲林係都市傳說來<br />\n<br />\n我飛左幾十次都係咁寄又唔見我出事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你菲林幾多度先～ 過400就開始會見到有影響（應該）"},{"pid":"503af47526cbb155e6c2b9824a1c37da94c8733b","tid":100922,"uid":12370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"上次關西機場番來<br />\n可以同佢講係菲林手持過關，佢會當住你面打開盒仔check一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb656c9c018af73be2fbd9b50a2acdb95336087","tid":100922,"uid":8909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話寄倉xray會炒菲林係都市傳說來<br />\n<br />\n我飛左幾十次都係咁寄又唔見我出事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你菲林幾多度先～ 過400就開始會見到有影響（應該）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔放check luggage <br />\n菲林唔過800 <br />\n過x ray 機唔多過5次<br />\n應該問題唔大<br />\n<br />\nTSA 話o既 (好似係)<br />\n<a href=\"http://filmadvance.com/2013/10/how-to-flying-with-film/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffilmadvance.com%2F2013%2F10%2Fhow-to-flying-with-film%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8ad3adf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://filmadvance.com/2013/10/how-to-flying-with-film/</a>"},{"pid":"94049e79f7b0b43b6398e9c5ae74c5fbd23b9972","tid":100922,"uid":74358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:09:17.000Z","msg":"其實唔使咁擔心, 過800，hand check, 唔過800，就咁放入hand carry , 乜事都冇"}]}